{"id":1239,"date":"2019-01-03T10:46:54","date_gmt":"2019-01-03T03:46:54","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/?p=1239"},"modified":"2019-01-03T10:47:10","modified_gmt":"2019-01-03T03:47:10","slug":"giai-phap-thong-gio-cho-nha-ong-hieu-qua-tiet-kiem-chi-phi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/giai-phap-thong-gio-cho-nha-ong-hieu-qua-tiet-kiem-chi-phi","title":{"rendered":"Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 cho nh\u00e0 \u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 &#8211; ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <strong>Thietkethicongdn.com<\/strong> xin gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/giai-phap-thong-gio-cho-nha-ong-hieu-qua-tiet-kiem-chi-phi\"><em><strong>Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 cho nh\u00e0 \u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 &#8211; ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/span> gi\u00fap ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 nh\u00e0 \u1edf l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1240 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/Gi\u1ea3i-ph\u00e1p-th\u00f4ng-gi\u00f3-cho-nh\u00e0-\u1ed1ng-hi\u1ec7u-qu\u1ea3-ti\u1ebft-ki\u1ec7m-chi-ph\u00ed.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 nh\u00e0 \u1edf ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m cho kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <strong>l\u01b0u th\u00f4ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c<\/strong>. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 khi <strong>l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00ed m\u1edb<\/strong>i t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0o, n\u00f3 s\u1ebd <strong>\u0111\u1ea9y l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00ed c\u0169<\/strong> ra kh\u1ecfi nh\u00e0 qua nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3. M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch l\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9, cung c\u1ea5p oxi v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng kh\u00ed cho con ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"Giai_phap_thong_gio_tu_nhien_cho_nha_ong\"><strong>1. Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean cho nh\u00e0 \u1ed1ng<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean cho nh\u00e0 \u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1edfi n\u00f3 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u1edf m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"Bo_tri_cua_nha_hop_ly\"><strong>a. B\u1ed1 tr\u00ed c\u1eeda nh\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1241 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/Gi\u1ea3i-ph\u00e1p-th\u00f4ng-gi\u00f3-cho-nh\u00e0-\u1ed1ng-hi\u1ec7u-qu\u1ea3-ti\u1ebft-ki\u1ec7m-chi-ph\u00ed1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"276\" \/><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><em>&gt;&gt;&gt; XEM NGAY\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/phong-ngu-co-2-cua-ra-vao-xet-theo-phong-thuy-la-tot-hay-xau\"><strong>Ph\u00f2ng Ng\u1ee7 C\u00f3 2 C\u1eeda Ra V\u00e0o &#8211; X\u00e9t theo phong th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t hay x\u1ea5u?<\/strong><\/a><\/span><\/em><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1eeda \u0111\u00f3n gi\u00f3 v\u00e0 c\u1eeda tho\u00e1t gi\u00f3 n\u1eb1m kh\u00e1c ph\u00eda nhau \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00f3 trong nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u01b0u th\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o v\u00e0 c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0y tr\u00ed v\u1edbi m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 cao. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a c\u0103n nh\u00e0.<\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li><strong>C\u1eeda \u0111\u00f3n gi\u00f3:<\/strong> Th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn, quay v\u1ec1 ph\u00ed h\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u00f3. N\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n t\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u00fat gi\u00f3.<\/li>\n<li><strong>C\u1eeda tho\u00e1t gi\u00f3:<\/strong>\u00a0\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao h\u01a1n c\u1eeda \u0111\u00f3n gi\u00f3 v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng chia l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1eeda nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea9y kh\u00ed c\u0169 ph\u00e2n t\u00e1n ra ngo\u00e0i\u00a0.\u00a0\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 \u1ed1ng h\u1eb9p n\u00ean thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1eeda tho\u00e1t gi\u00f3 \u1edf ngay ph\u00eda sau nh\u00e0.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1edf c\u1eeda \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y gi\u00f3 v\u00e0o nh\u00e0.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"Lam_gieng_troi_trong_nha\"><strong>b. L\u00e0m gi\u1ebfng tr\u1eddi trong nh\u00e0<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1242 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/Gi\u1ea3i-ph\u00e1p-th\u00f4ng-gi\u00f3-cho-nh\u00e0-\u1ed1ng-hi\u1ec7u-qu\u1ea3-ti\u1ebft-ki\u1ec7m-chi-ph\u00ed2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"418\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; N\u00ean thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf cho nh\u00e0 \u1ed1ng m\u1ed9t gi\u1ebfng tr\u1eddi m\u1edf thay v\u00ec gi\u1ebfng tr\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3ng. B\u1edfi ngo\u00e0i t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng l\u1ea5y s\u00e1ng, gi\u1ebfng tr\u1edd m\u1edf c\u00f2n c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ed1ng th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 th\u00f4ng qua m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; Trong m\u1ed9t c\u0103n h\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf 1, 2 hay nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ebfng tr\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3. T\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng gi\u1ebfng tr\u1eddi nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ed5ng tho\u00e1t gi\u00f3 hay v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00fat gi\u00f3, v\u00e0 tho\u00e1t gi\u00f3.<\/p>\n<blockquote><p><em>&gt;&gt;&gt; XEM TH\u00caM\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/giai-phap-thiet-ke-nha-ong-khuat-trong-hem-toi-dep\">&#8220;GI\u1ea2I PH\u00c1P THI\u1ebeT K\u1ebe&#8221; Nh\u00e0 \u1ed0ng khu\u1ea5t trong h\u1ebbm t\u1ed1i \u0111\u1eb9p 2018<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p class=\"text-container subheading -mt-line- -centered-\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"Tan_dung_khoang_thong_nhau_giua_cac_phong\"><strong>c. T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng kho\u1ea3ng th\u00f4ng nhau gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1244 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/Gi\u1ea3i-ph\u00e1p-th\u00f4ng-gi\u00f3-cho-nh\u00e0-\u1ed1ng-hi\u1ec7u-qu\u1ea3-ti\u1ebft-ki\u1ec7m-chi-ph\u00ed3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" \/><\/p>\n<div class=\"ideabook--item-photo -mt-line-\">\n<div class=\"photo\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"ideabook--item-photo -mt-line-\">\n<div class=\"photo\">\n<div class=\"photo--information bordered\" data-author-locale=\"vn\" data-author-professional=\"true\" data-author-id=\"3888257\" data-author-message-path=\"\/users_route\/3888257\/messages\/new\" data-photo-id=\"2164632\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; N\u1ebfu trong m\u1ed9t c\u0103n nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nhi\u1ec1u c\u1eeda nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1eafn th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong nh\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 m\u00e0 l\u01b0u th\u00f4ng. Do \u0111\u00f3, n\u00ean t\u1ea1o nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng gian th\u00f4ng nhau gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng ho\u1eb7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m b\u00ecnh phong ng\u0103n ph\u00f2ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap d\u00f2ng kh\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng su\u1ed1t.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2. Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p c\u01a1 h\u1ecdc<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 m\u00e0 v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 th\u00ec c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u01a1 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0. C\u00e1 ba h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 c\u01a1 kh\u00ed c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee7 d\u1ee5ng:<\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 ki\u1ec3u th\u1ed5i<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 ki\u1ec3u h\u00fat<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 ki\u1ec3u k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1245\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1245\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1245 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/Gi\u1ea3i-ph\u00e1p-th\u00f4ng-gi\u00f3-cho-nh\u00e0-\u1ed1ng-hi\u1ec7u-qu\u1ea3-ti\u1ebft-ki\u1ec7m-chi-ph\u00ed4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"303\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1245\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>(H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng gi\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ecdc)<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Thietkethicongdn.com xin gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 cho nh\u00e0 \u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 &#8211; ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed gi\u00fap ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i nh\u00e9! Th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":1240,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1239"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.co